    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……大丈夫か？　ずっとため息をついてるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Are you okay? You've been sighing constantly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5795692164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "私の役柄が単なる『少女A』だなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calling my role simply \"Girl A\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7643765011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ため息もつきたくなりますわ……\nせっかく張り切っていましたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It makes me want to sigh…\nI was so excited and all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.1151926397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、まぁ初めてのドラマなんだ\n端役なのは仕方ないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it's your first drama after all.\nIt's inevitable for minor roles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.1669838308
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "端役どころじゃありませんわ！\nただ映り込むだけですのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just a minor role!\nI'm literally just in the background!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.1049430409
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "しかも一瞬ですわ！　冒頭で発見される死体の方が\n長く映るだけマシですわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And it's just for a split second! I'd rather be the dead body at the beginning…\nAt least that would get more screen time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、脚本によると、死体はうつぶせで倒れているから\n顔が全然映らない。少女Aの方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ according to the script‚ the dead body is face down.\nYou won't even see the face. Being Girl A is better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、それなら少女Aの方が……って\nなぜそんな低いレベルで競わなければなりませんの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ then being Girl A… Wait!\nWhy do we have to compete on such a low level!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "す、すまない。少しでも元気づけようと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm sorry. I was trying to cheer you up a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "かえって傷口をえぐってますわよ！\n……お気持ちは嬉しいですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're just digging the wound deeper!\n…I appreciate the sentiment though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、こんなことなら、みんなに連絡なんて\nしなければ良かったですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ if it's going to be like this‚\nI shouldn't have contacted anyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は寮でリアルタイムで、みんな一緒に観る！\n……って言ってましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei said they're all going to watch together\nin the dorm in real-time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "きっと放送を観ても、いつ私が出たのか分からずに\n気まずい空気になるのがオチですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure when they watch the broadcast‚ they won't even know when I appeared…\nIt's going to be awkward…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（いい経験になれば、くらいの気持ちで勧めたのが）\n（裏目に出てしまったな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I suggested it with the mindset that it might be a good experience.）\n（It seems to have backfired…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、どうしたらいいのでしょう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh‚ what should I do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（すずの性格を考えて、最初に役のことを）\n（話すべきだったな……。こうなったら――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Considering Suzu's personality‚ I should have talked to her about the role initially.）\n（… In this situation‚ maybe I can…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……でもすずなら、これをチャンスに変えることが\n出来るかもしれない。いや、出来る",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But if it's Suzu‚ you might be able to turn this\ninto an opportunity. No‚ you can do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "何を言っていますの？\n私はセリフのない、少女Aですのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying?\nI'm just Girl A without any lines‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "すずにはセリフはなくても\nアイドルとしての華があるじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even without lines‚\nSuzu has the radiance of an idol‚ doesn't she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "すずが映れば、それだけで視聴者は注目する\n画面に釘付けになるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Suzu appears‚ viewers will naturally pay attention.\nThey'll be glued to the screen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.9137411557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_02-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-Is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
